                    <span>Very moving and award winning. You actually feel like you are traveling with the doomed party. I love the aerial views of the terrain they fought thru to get to California. I had to watch this as a AP History student in high school. You learn a whole ton about manifest destiny as well. To think, these people literally walked across the United States. </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An excellent account of a terrible event</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
