                    <span>I too remember seeing this documentary on England's Channel 4 and was immediately impressed by the understated tone that let the central characters speak for themselves and the horror that slowly unravels as the snow continues to fall. <br>It's rare to find a product that receives so many five stars and be so justified.</span>
                  
              
